    "description": "<strong>Welcome To Uplife!</strong><br><br>Here you can experience new type of economic simulation life in Upcity. You can get a job for your daily needs or create own business empire to become richest man in the world. Pay your taxes, expand the business and be a good citizen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/25d05e99554148f83ef40f3f2ee96d09.avif?t=1682449524\" width=500 height=69 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/57317f80d742fbb07d3b5496d8764de8.poster.avif?t=1682449524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/57317f80d742fbb07d3b5496d8764de8.webm?t=1682449524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/57317f80d742fbb07d3b5496d8764de8.mp4?t=1682449524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready to start your new Uplife in Upcity! Here you can live a well spent life as you wish. Start from scratch and become your own business empire owner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/ec4bd176fbd04346072defd3a26d1d49.webp?t=1682449524\" width=498 height=56 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/3105aedcd088445f7ac5bdaed2b19d9f.poster.avif?t=1682449524\" width=664 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221450/extras/3105aedcd088445f7ac5bdaed2b19d9f.webm?t=1682449524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=